                <td bgcolor="#37437B" valign="top" width="100" nowrap><font color="white" face="verdana" size="2"><b>Derugash</b></font></td>
                <td bgcolor="#37437B" valign="top" width="100%"><font color="white" face="verdana" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;01/22/2004&nbsp;: 1:13:43 PM</small><hr size="1"><span class="spnMessageText"> I have critical affliction lvl 2 on Beta, and played around with it a little. Using just embracing darkness I killed a couple of mobs and parsed the results with JALP. (Thanks Reepr, awesome prog)<br />This is by no means a way to get an exact percentage for CA, but it will give an idea.. I wouldnt panic just yet since the skill might be broken and not giving the right percentage, but needless to say ive been feedbacking about this low crit chance. <br /><br /><img src="http://home.planet.nl/~pete0420/3d/critdot/1.jpg" border="0"><br /><img src="http://home.planet.nl/~pete0420/3d/critdot/2.jpg" border="0"><br /><br /></span></font></td>
